name: 查理·斯托里
introduction: Charlie Storey is a Canadian actor based in Toronto. She began her career as a commercial actor at the age of 6 and quickly fell in love with being in front of the camera. Charlie expanded to film and television in 2021, starring in two episodes of Eli Roth Presents: A Ghost Ruined My Life. In 2022, Charlie landed her first principal roles starring in Urban Legend (Discovery +) and as Isobel in the Reel One Entertainment movie, Sister Dating Swap (to be released in 2023). Charlie's first theatrical debut is set for November 2023, as part of the cast of Tristar Pictures, Thanksgiving.
